      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Fortunately, each of you has skills that prove particularly useful for
    your survival. Philemon is agile and discreet: he can travel long distances without
    being detected. Linow is a survival expert, capable of fishing with his bare
    hands. Nils is a mountain of muscle, able to face any danger.


    When all
    your character are moved, you need to reunite them to camp for the night, eat
    food and craft supplies.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
