  m_text: 'To move your characters, use the A/Q and D key for the left/right, and
    W/Z and S for top/bottom, in addition to the Q/A and E keys to select your side
    (Bottom Left is Q + S on a qwerty keyboard, Top Right is E + W...). When the
    correct tile is highlighted, use enter.


    Esc allows to go to the pause menu
    where this window is also available. '
